Excellent! Now I have all the information needed. Let me provide a comprehensive report on the iskrib_v3 visual design language and component patterns:

---

## ISKRIB_V3 VISUAL DESIGN LANGUAGE & COMPONENT PATTERNS

### 1. CSS DESIGN TOKENS & COLOR PALETTE

**Global CSS Variables** (`client/src/index.css`)

**Light Mode:**
- Background Colors:
  - `--bg-primary: #FAF9F6` (main background)
  - `--bg-secondary: #F3F1ED` (secondary surfaces)
  - `--bg-elevated: #FFFFFF` (elevated cards)
  - `--bg-card: #FEFEFE` (card backgrounds)
  - `--bg-glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.55)` (glass morphism)
  - `--bg-glass-border: rgba(200,180,150,0.2)` (glass border)
  - `--bg-pill: rgba(120,100,80,0.06)` (pill/tag backgrounds)
  - `--bg-overlay: rgba(250,249,246,0.3)` (modal/overlay)
  - `--bg-backdrop: rgba(250,249,246,0.75)` (backdrop filter)
  - `--bg-backdrop-heavy: rgba(250,249,246,0.85)`

- Text Colors:
  - `--text-primary: #1A1612` (main text)
  - `--text-heading: #12100D` (headings)
  - `--text-secondary: #6B6560` (secondary text)
  - `--text-body: #8A8480` (body text)
  - `--text-muted: #A8A29E` (muted)
  - `--text-faint: #C0BBB5` (very light)
  - `--text-separator: #D9D4CE` (dividers)

- Accent Colors:
  - `--accent-purple: #C4943E` (primary accent/gold)
  - `--accent-dark: #1A1612` (dark accent)
  - `--accent-sage: #8A9E7A` (sage green)
  - `--accent-amber: #D4A853` (warm amber)

- Border & Shadow:
  - `--border-light: rgba(120,100,80,0.12)`
  - `--border-card: rgba(120,100,80,0.08)`
  - `--shadow-card: 0 1px 4px rgba(80,60,40,0.06), 0 4px 16px rgba(80,60,40,0.04)`
  - `--shadow-modal: 0 8px 32px rgba(80,60,40,0.12)`
  - `--shadow-dropdown: 0 4px 16px rgba(80,60,40,0.1), 0 0 0 1px rgba(120,100,80,0.06)`

- Special Colors:
  - `--color-danger: #DC2626` (errors)
  - `--color-success: #16A34A` (success)
  - `--loader-color: #C4943E` (spinners)

**Dark Mode** (`[data-theme="dark"]`):
- Background inverted with muted versions (primary becomes `#0C0C0C`)
- Text lightened (primary becomes `#F0EBE3`)
- Accents brightened (amber becomes `#E0BA6A`)
- Maintains same semantic structure with adjusted opacity/brightness

---

### 2. TYPOGRAPHY & FONT SYSTEM

**Font Families:**
- `--font-serif: "Lora", Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif` (body content)
